cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC 

This paper proposes a method for sketch-to-image translation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The method also involves the use of a GAN-based approach, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper focuses on creating a user-friendly interface for novice users, which relates to the human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
